      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. it feels like the real me—the one with all the dreams and the spark—died a lifetime ago. now i'm just... going through the motions. like a ghost or a walking corpse. just a shell of what i was supposed to be.",
