    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... why should i \"stay here\" in this state? staying feels like it's just prolonging a funeral that happened years ago. it feels pointless to keep pushing a body that's already empty. doesn't it seem exhausting to everyone else, too? just watching someone pretend to be alive?",
